        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Confiscating Corrupt Criminal Proceeds (CCCP) Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes forfeited property owned by a Russian or Belarusian national to be transferred to the U.S. Agency for International Development and used to provide humanitarian assistance to the people of Ukraine.</p>]]>
        </text>
